Specially designed for dogs, this soap-free and pH-balanced formula ensures your pup's coat stays clean, soft, and smelling fresh, without harmful chemicals.
Description:
Earthbath Sweet Orange Dirty Dog Shampoo is a luxurious grooming solution crafted to eliminate tough odors, grime, and fur stains while moisturizing your dog’s coat. Infused with the natural oil of orange peels (d'Limonene), this shampoo acts as an effective degreaser and deodorizer, perfect for outdoor dogs who love to play in the dirt. Formulated with natural and organic ingredients like coconut-based cleansers and olive oil squalene, it soothes common skin irritations and helps relieve itching caused by flea bites. The soap-free, paraben-free, and pH-balanced formula ensures a gentle yet thorough clean that leaves your dog’s coat shiny, soft, and plush, with a vibrant orange scent. Ideal for all life stages, it is biodegradable, cruelty-free, and crafted with your pet's health and the environment in mind. Not suitable for cats due to possible sensitivities.

 

Features

 

  • Moisturizing shampoo with natural orange peel oil

  • Effectively removes odor, grease, and stains

  • Contains d'Limonene, coconut cleansers, and olive oil squalene

  • Paraben-free, soap-free, dye-free, and non-toxic

  • pH-balanced for dog skin; safe for all life stages

  • Biodegradable and cruelty-free since 1995

  • Not recommended for use on cats

Name: Gigwi Zoomin Friends Raccon
Short description: The GiGwi Zoomin Friends Racoon Dog Toy is a durable and engaging plush toy featuring a soft body, textured natural rubber back, and a built-in squeaker. Designed to satisfy your dog’s play instincts, it helps with dental hygiene and offers fun both indoors and outdoors.
Description:
The GiGwi Zoomin Friends Racoon Dog Toy blends durability, comfort, and interactive fun into a single, well-crafted playmate for your furry friend. Designed with intricate embroidery, it offers a lifelike appearance that stimulates your dog’s natural hunting instincts. The soft plush body ensures gentle play, while the natural rubber back adds strength and longevity, making it suitable for active chewers. The textured rubber surface also promotes dental health by gently cleaning your dog’s teeth during play. A built-in squeaker provides extra excitement, grabbing your dog's attention and encouraging longer engagement. Whether your dog is playing inside or outside, this versatile toy is designed for dynamic fun, hiding, chasing, or comforting cuddles. Lightweight yet sturdy, it's perfect for dogs that enjoy interactive or solo play.

 

Features

 

  • Realistic animal design with intricate embroidery

  • Built-in squeaker keeps your dog entertained

  • Soft plush body offers gentle comfort

  • Natural rubber back adds durability and promotes dental hygiene

  • Ideal for indoor and outdoor interactive play

  • Stimulates natural hunting behavior
